 {"id": "franken_networkx-cflowbetw", "title": "REVIEW: [HIGH] current_flow_betweenness_centrality diverged ~2.5x from nx across all nodes", "description": "The Rust current_flow_betweenness_centrality_rust produced scores that differed from nx's by a factor of ~2.5x across karate_club_graph nodes (fnx=0.189 vs nx=0.486 on node 0; ratio ~2.57). The divergence held both normalized and unnormalized and across all tested nodes \u2014 not numerical noise but a different normalization constant or flow-splitting formula than nx's random-walk current-flow interpretation. Also the Rust path silently ignored the ``solver`` and ``dtype`` kwargs that nx supports. Delegate to nx for exact parity.", "status": "closed", "priority": 2, "issue_type": "bug", "created_at": "2026-04-24T21:30:00.000000000Z", "created_by": "cc-networkx", "updated_at": "2026-04-24T21:30:00.000000000Z", "closed_at": "2026-04-24T21:30:00.000000000Z", "close_reason": "Delegate to nx via _current_flow_betweenness_impl", "source_repo": ".", "compaction_level": 0, "original_size": 0}
 {"id": "franken_networkx-estradaweighted", "title": "REVIEW: [HIGH] estrada_index used WEIGHTED adjacency spectrum; nx uses UNWEIGHTED", "description": "nx.estrada_index computes the index via ``sum(subgraph_centrality(G).values())``, where subgraph_centrality internally uses ``to_numpy_array(G, weight=None)`` \u2014 the UNWEIGHTED adjacency matrix. fnx's local implementation used ``sum(exp(adjacency_spectrum(G)))`` where ``adjacency_spectrum`` defaults to the WEIGHTED adjacency. On karate_club_graph (which has weight attrs on every edge) this produced fnx=2.65e9 vs nx=1041 \u2014 a ratio of ~2.5 million. Small unweighted graphs (K3, K5, C5, path) happened to match because their unweighted/weighted adjacency are identical. Reimplemented as ``sum(subgraph_centrality(G).values())`` to match nx's formulation (mathematically equivalent to sum of exp(eigenvalues) of the unweighted A).", "status": "closed", "priority": 2, "issue_type": "bug", "created_at": "2026-04-24T22:00:00.000000000Z", "created_by": "cc-networkx", "updated_at": "2026-04-24T22:00:00.000000000Z", "closed_at": "2026-04-24T22:00:00.000000000Z", "close_reason": "Match nx formulation: sum(subgraph_centrality(G).values())", "source_repo": ".", "compaction_level": 0, "original_size": 0}
